description:
An enhanced version of the http://anidb.net/ch89525 [Kamiki Burning Gundam] to which http://anidb.net/ch68681 [Sekai] has applied further customizations. With its offense and defense improved by the wing-shaped unit on its back, known as the "Wing Burning," it can let loose the ultimate secret of the Kamiki Gunpla school of kenpo.
Source: Official page
name: SBG-E01 Shin Burning Gundam
